<HEADLINE> Dos Santos, Savimbi to Meet in Angolan Capital </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUANDA, November 12 (Xinhua) -- Angolan President Eduardo dos
Santos will meet Jonas Savimbi, the leader of the opposition
National Union for the Total Independence of Angola (UNITA) late
this month in the capital Luanda.
</P>
<P>
This was announced here today by a spokesman of the Angolan
Presidential Office, Aldemiro da Conceicao, who added that
President dos Santos and the opposition leader Savimbi contacted
by telephone on Tuesday to fix the place for the incoming meeting
and other details.
