made in the full implementation of the Lusaka peace agreement
before the summit to create a good political atmosphere for its
success.
</P>
<P>
This will be the fifth meeting between the leaders of the two
Angolan warring sides since the Lusaka peace agreement was signed
in 1994 and also the first one to be held in their own country.
</P>
