Suresh Desai told reporters the political situation in the
country does not warrant the international intervntion.
</P>
<P>
The minister said Zambian leaders have not failed to solve
their own problems.
</P>
<P>
Kaunda is having a marathon trip abroad to lobby the
international community to stop assistance to the Zambian
government. 
