gathering of foreign dignitaries. Around 50 heads of state,
including the Gulf Arab states, have been invited to the
convention.
</P>
<P>
The UAE, which has a territorial dispute with Iran, is the
fifth leg of Kharrazi's tour which has taken him to Saudi Arabia,
Kuwait, Bahrain and Qatar, and will also take him to Oman.
