</P>
<P>
Frankfurt: min. 6 degrees C., max. 8 degrees C., overcast to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Paris: min. 4 degrees C., max. 8 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
