<HEADLINE> Sri Lanka Lacks Trained Housemaids for Overseas </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
COLOMBO, November 13 (Xinhua) -- There are at least 8,000 job
opportunities in Singapore for trained housemaids, but it is
difficult to find qualified applicants in Sri Lanka, Chairman of
the Bureau of Foreign Employment Kapil Abayaratne said today.
</P>
<P>
Abayaratne said these jobs are available for Sri Lankan
housemaids who can speak English.
</P>
