arms being used like several years ago," Foreign Minister Ali
Alatas said here on Wednesday. To increase sanctions on Iraq was
not the answer to the problem but would even complicate the
situation, and the sanction imposed so far had not met any target
or fulfilled the hopes but had caused grief among the civilian
population, including women, children and old people, he said.
(Indonesia-Iraq) 
