<HEADLINE> Zimbabwe's Cotton Collection Exceeds Target </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, November 13 (Xinhua) -- The Cotton Company of Zimbabwe
(COTTCO), the country's largest ginner and marketer of cotton,said
it has this year collected over 192,000 tonnes of cotton seed,
exceeding its target by nearly 12,000 tonnes.
</P>
<P>
A company spokesman said Wednesday that the 192,738 tonnes of
cotton seed collected represented 96 percent of its ginning
capacity of 200,000 tonnes.
</P>
<P>
